WEBVTT

00:10.552 --> 00:11.929
♪ You could do it solo ♪

00:11.929 --> 00:13.931
♪ But then you'd be all by yourself ♪

00:13.931 --> 00:16.391
♪ Yo! So, it'd be more fun
To share this one ♪

00:16.391 --> 00:18.018
♪ With someone else ♪

00:18.018 --> 00:21.647
♪ Together we will soar
Across the sky and beyond ♪

00:21.647 --> 00:23.232
♪ So turn up your voice ♪

00:23.774 --> 00:25.526
♪ Stand up and sing along ♪

00:25.526 --> 00:27.569
♪ All different voices
Everybody now! ♪

00:27.569 --> 00:29.404
♪ Our melodies ringing ♪

00:29.404 --> 00:31.323
♪ We're livin' in harmony ♪

00:31.323 --> 00:33.242
♪ Yeah, we're livin' in harmony ♪

00:33.242 --> 00:37.037
♪ Our song is much stronger
With every Troll singing ♪

00:37.037 --> 00:39.498
♪ We're livin' in harmony ♪♪

00:43.418 --> 00:46.421
♪

00:49.174 --> 00:50.384
‐ No, no.

00:50.384 --> 00:51.927
Synth, you're flat.

00:51.927 --> 00:54.137
Holly, you could stand to be sharper.

00:55.013 --> 00:58.141
‐ My banner hangin' could be sharper?

00:58.267 --> 00:59.851
‐ Sharper, Holly! Sharper!

01:00.227 --> 01:01.103
‐ Ah!
‐ Ah!

01:02.896 --> 01:03.855
‐ Oh!

01:04.856 --> 01:06.733
‐ See, now that's too sharp.

01:07.276 --> 01:08.694
[ Holly growls ]

01:08.944 --> 01:10.404
Oh, I do apologize.

01:10.404 --> 01:12.281
I just want everything to be perfect

01:12.281 --> 01:14.825
when my dear brother
Forte Crescendo arrives.

01:15.117 --> 01:16.868
We've always been ever so close…

01:17.286 --> 01:20.080
but I worry that since I moved
to TrollsTopia,

01:20.080 --> 01:23.125
the distance might be weakening
our special bond.

01:23.667 --> 01:25.043
‐ Aw.
‐ Aw.

01:25.419 --> 01:27.129
‐ Yes, I know it's adorable.

01:27.337 --> 01:29.673
But you see how important this visit is.

01:29.840 --> 01:32.509
Forte and I must bond like never before

01:32.509 --> 01:34.636
so that, by the time he's ready to leave,

01:35.012 --> 01:38.974
our connection will be strong enough
to see us through our time apart.

01:41.143 --> 01:42.144
‐ Pardon me, sir.

01:42.144 --> 01:44.479
Do you happen to know
where I might find a Troll

01:44.479 --> 01:46.189
by the name of Dante Crescendo?

01:46.523 --> 01:48.650
‐ Dante Crescendo you say?

01:48.859 --> 01:50.068
Not ringing a bell.

01:50.068 --> 01:53.530
Perhaps if you detailed
his finer characteristics.

01:53.739 --> 01:55.240
‐ Let's see, uh…

01:55.240 --> 01:59.745
sophisticated, talented,
easy on the eyes…?

02:00.078 --> 02:02.372
Oh, wait! I'm describing
his younger brother!

02:02.581 --> 02:03.623
[ laughing ]

02:03.623 --> 02:05.125
‐ Brother!
‐ Brother!

02:05.125 --> 02:06.501
[ laughing ]

02:06.877 --> 02:09.838
‐ Dearest sibling,
it is so good to see you.

02:10.297 --> 02:11.214
‐ Come, brother,

02:11.214 --> 02:14.259
let me introduce you to some
of my closest companions.

02:14.259 --> 02:18.513
‐ Ah, you must be
the relentlessly positive Poppy

02:18.513 --> 02:21.058
and the "Unsinkable Holly Darlin'"

02:21.058 --> 02:24.895
whose hospitality exceeds
even her own impressive bouffant.

02:25.270 --> 02:30.192
And that would make you the Techno Troll
Dante has told me so much about, Synth.

02:30.359 --> 02:32.235
Pleased to make your acquaintance.

02:32.235 --> 02:34.905
‐ Ah, bro, you don't need to make me
an acquaintance.

02:34.905 --> 02:36.239
I just ate lunch!

02:36.239 --> 02:37.157
‐ Uh…

02:37.157 --> 02:38.533
‐ Yo! Before I forget.

02:38.533 --> 02:43.121
On behalf of all the Techno Trolls,
I wanna invite you to tonight's rave!

02:44.122 --> 02:46.625
‐ Pray tell, what is a "rave"?

02:46.958 --> 02:48.752
‐ Oh, you gotta come check it!

02:49.002 --> 02:51.838
We play the sickest music
and dance 'til dawn.

02:52.130 --> 02:56.551
In fact, allow me to drop ya
a lil' sneakity peekity…

02:57.052 --> 02:59.262
♪

02:59.262 --> 03:00.347
[ gasp ]

03:00.347 --> 03:01.515
♪

03:01.515 --> 03:03.725
‐ I've never heard anything like it.

03:03.725 --> 03:06.395
The syncopation!
The thumping bass!

03:06.603 --> 03:10.774
It is, indeed, quite "sick."

03:10.941 --> 03:13.694
‐ Hmm, yes, practically nauseating.

03:13.902 --> 03:16.988
But I'm afraid Forte and I
will be spending his entire stay

03:16.988 --> 03:20.242
doing our favorite brother
bonding past time,

03:20.242 --> 03:21.535
composing symphonies.

03:21.785 --> 03:23.203
Isn't that right, Forte?

03:24.413 --> 03:25.372
Forte?

03:25.580 --> 03:28.750
‐ Oh, oh, yes, of course, composing.

03:28.959 --> 03:32.504
Many thanks
for the sneakitypeakity, Sir Synth.

03:32.963 --> 03:36.675
I would have liked to have heard more
of your Techno music.

03:37.843 --> 03:40.011
Yes, I would have liked that very much.

03:40.011 --> 03:41.680
[ bowel sound ]

03:42.097 --> 03:43.640
‐ Oh, man!

03:43.974 --> 03:46.268
I shoulda taken him up
on that acquaintance.

03:46.268 --> 03:47.853
♪

03:48.311 --> 03:50.730
‐ Brother, for this symphony
we're composing:

03:50.730 --> 03:53.024
do you know what would be
a devilish follow up

03:53.024 --> 03:54.860
to the opening allegro movement?

03:55.152 --> 03:56.987
Another allegro movement.

03:57.737 --> 04:00.115
I know, I'm so bad.

04:00.449 --> 04:03.618
[ Forte imitates techno music ]

04:03.618 --> 04:05.912
Are you all right, beloved sibling?

04:05.912 --> 04:08.081
‐ Oh, well, actually,

04:08.081 --> 04:11.877
I can't seem to get that "tech‐no" beat
out of my head, brother.

04:11.877 --> 04:12.919
[ nervous laugh ]

04:13.670 --> 04:15.881
‐ Oh, worry not, it's tea time.

04:15.881 --> 04:19.718
Nothing gets one's creativity flowing
like a spot of Earl Glitter

04:19.718 --> 04:21.720
and unnecessarily small sandwiches!

04:21.720 --> 04:22.679
[ laughing ]

04:25.891 --> 04:28.810
[ techno music ]

04:33.148 --> 04:35.901
Well, the sandwiches
aren't as tiny as I'd hoped but‐‐

04:36.485 --> 04:37.319
Brother?

04:37.527 --> 04:38.403
Brother?

04:39.488 --> 04:40.572
[ humming ]

04:40.572 --> 04:42.824
DANTE:
Oh! This is a disaster!

04:42.824 --> 04:43.658
‐ Huh?

04:44.618 --> 04:46.578
‐ An utter disaster!

04:46.578 --> 04:48.163
‐ Dante, what's wrong?

04:48.163 --> 04:49.247
‐ It's Forte!

04:49.247 --> 04:53.335
He's left our brother bonding
to go rave in Techno Lagoon!

04:53.502 --> 04:55.962
It's all detailed in the notes
he wrote me!

04:55.962 --> 04:57.506
‐ "Notes"? Don't you mean‐‐?

04:58.048 --> 05:00.258
Oh, no, you really do mean "notes."

05:00.550 --> 05:01.468
‐ Yes!

05:01.468 --> 05:03.011
And as you can plainly read,

05:03.011 --> 05:07.140
it says my brother has left me
during our very special time together.

05:07.140 --> 05:08.183
[ sobbing ]

05:08.183 --> 05:12.145
Apparently, our unbreakable bond
is breakable after all.

05:12.813 --> 05:16.775
‐ Dante, look, Forte may be
expressing new interests,

05:16.775 --> 05:18.860
but he's not a new person.

05:19.236 --> 05:22.531
He's your brother
and nothing will ever change that.

05:22.989 --> 05:25.116
‐ You're… sure?

05:25.784 --> 05:26.868
‐ Absolutely.

05:27.285 --> 05:29.329
But hey, don't take my word for it.

05:29.579 --> 05:31.998
Let's go down there,
so you can ask him yourself.

05:32.582 --> 05:34.209
‐ Down… there…?

05:34.626 --> 05:37.254
♪

05:37.420 --> 05:39.714
‐ See! Isn't this place amazing?

05:39.714 --> 05:42.342
‐ Oh, yes, very charming‐‐

05:42.342 --> 05:44.219
what, with the Troll‐niverous fish

05:44.219 --> 05:47.931
and the bottomless trench
from whence there's no return.

05:48.557 --> 05:50.976
Why, oh, why didn't I come down
here sooner?

05:51.351 --> 05:52.310
[ gasp ]

05:52.769 --> 05:55.605
[ Trolls cheering ]

05:55.981 --> 05:56.982
Heavens!

05:56.982 --> 05:59.901
How will I locate Forte
amidst all this frivolity?

06:00.235 --> 06:02.612
Forte! Forte!

06:02.988 --> 06:05.699
‐ Yo, Classico! Wanna shuffle?

06:05.991 --> 06:08.827
‐ Oop, apologies,
fellow Trolls‐Topian but no,

06:08.827 --> 06:10.412
I'm just here to find my broth‐‐

06:10.412 --> 06:12.163
‐ Hey! Let's go, maestro!

06:12.414 --> 06:13.790
‐ Excuse me, no!

06:14.207 --> 06:17.210
Can 't you see I am trying
to forge a path?

06:17.544 --> 06:23.008
‐ Aw! This Classical Troll's throwin' down
a hot new dance move!

06:23.008 --> 06:24.676
♪ I'm trying to forge a path! ♪

06:24.676 --> 06:26.261
♪ I'm trying to forge a path! ♪

06:26.261 --> 06:28.889
‐ Stop!
I must attend to my brother!

06:29.097 --> 06:30.640
♪ I must attend to my brother! ♪

06:30.765 --> 06:32.475
♪ I must attend to my brother! ♪

06:32.475 --> 06:35.228
‐ Gah! Poppy, will you please
explain to them‐‐

06:35.228 --> 06:36.146
[ gasp ]

06:36.146 --> 06:37.772
♪ I must attend to my brother! ♪

06:37.772 --> 06:39.441
♪ I must attend to my brother! ♪♪

06:40.108 --> 06:42.319
‐ Sorry. It is a very hot move.

06:42.611 --> 06:47.157
‐ Yes, but hot as it may be,
I am having no success finding Forte!

06:47.157 --> 06:49.534
TECHNO BOUNCER:
Yo, you're lookin' for Forte?

06:50.952 --> 06:52.954
He's in the VIP section.

06:52.954 --> 06:54.164
‐ Oh…
‐ Oh…

06:54.164 --> 06:55.415
‐ Woah, woah, woah.

06:55.415 --> 06:59.753
Absolutely no one gets in there
without a VIP pass.

07:00.670 --> 07:02.339
Which is why you need these!

07:02.672 --> 07:06.217
K, have fun, love you!

07:06.885 --> 07:09.888
♪

07:11.681 --> 07:12.599
‐ Forte!

07:12.807 --> 07:16.686
At last, we can return to the surface
and resume our composition.

07:16.686 --> 07:17.854
‐ Yo!

07:17.854 --> 07:20.065
Meh‐meh‐meh‐meh‐meh‐meh!

07:20.065 --> 07:21.066
[ gasp ]

07:21.858 --> 07:24.361
What up, my bro‐bro
from the same mo‐mo?

07:24.361 --> 07:28.573
I was hopin' you'd come down
to share in all the delicious plur!

07:28.948 --> 07:31.701
‐ Peace love unity respect!
‐ Peace love unity respect!

07:31.701 --> 07:33.161
‐ Hey‐o!
‐ Hey‐o!

07:33.620 --> 07:36.206
‐ "Bro"? "Plur"? "Hey‐o"?

07:36.331 --> 07:37.957
Forte, you've gone…

07:38.416 --> 07:39.959
full rave?

07:40.919 --> 07:43.588
‐ Ha‐ha! You got that right, boy!

07:44.172 --> 07:46.299
BOTH:
Meh‐meh‐meh‐meh‐meh‐meh!

07:46.299 --> 07:47.967
[ funny noises ]

07:47.967 --> 07:48.802
[ gasp ]

07:49.803 --> 07:53.014
‐ Poppy! When I said my bond
with Forte was in jeopardy,

07:53.014 --> 07:56.351
you promised he wasn't becoming
a new person! But look!

07:56.351 --> 07:59.145
[ funny noises ]

07:59.145 --> 08:01.606
‐ Dante, he's just having some fun.

08:01.815 --> 08:05.443
Now, I know you want to get back
to composing with Forte right away,

08:05.443 --> 08:08.697
so just take a deep breath
and calmly tell him that.

08:09.239 --> 08:10.573
[ deep breath ]

08:10.573 --> 08:12.283
[ funny noises ]

08:12.283 --> 08:14.285
‐ Forte‐‐ um, Forte‐‐

08:14.828 --> 08:17.706
Do you think we could go somewhere
and have a word?

08:17.706 --> 08:20.458
‐ All right, you got it, Big D!

08:21.334 --> 08:23.253
‐ Oh!
‐ Oh!

08:23.545 --> 08:25.422
‐ This song is the banger, yo!

08:25.422 --> 08:29.175
Can we "have a word"
after the beat drops?

08:29.634 --> 08:34.389
‐ Uh, well, I suppose we could stay
just for one beat drop.

08:34.681 --> 08:36.099
[ laughing ]

08:39.227 --> 08:44.274
♪

08:44.649 --> 08:46.317
‐ Wait for it.
‐ Wait for it.

08:46.818 --> 08:48.903
‐ Wait for it.
‐ Wait for it.

08:49.320 --> 08:51.740
‐ Wait for it.
‐ Wait for it.

08:52.282 --> 08:54.617
‐ Wait for it.
