08:55.243 --> 08:57.412
‐ Wait for it.
‐ Wait for it.

08:57.412 --> 09:01.041
‐ Just drop the infernal beat.

09:01.499 --> 09:03.585
‐ Wait for it.
‐ Wait for it.

09:03.585 --> 09:04.544
‐ Enough!

09:06.171 --> 09:10.842
If you refuse to drop the beat,
then there shall be no beats at all!

09:15.346 --> 09:16.556
EVERYBODY:
Oh…

09:17.682 --> 09:19.392
‐ Give back the banger, bro!

09:23.146 --> 09:26.316
‐ A pox upon thee,
you brotherstealing beats!

09:26.816 --> 09:29.778
Into the bottomless trench with you!

09:29.778 --> 09:31.821
[ evil laugh ]

09:31.821 --> 09:32.906
FORTE:
Dante!

09:35.408 --> 09:36.451
DANTE:
Forte?

09:37.952 --> 09:40.663
What… what am I doing?

09:41.539 --> 09:43.833
I've gotten quite carried away, haven't I?

09:45.210 --> 09:46.795
I'm so sorry, everyone.

09:46.795 --> 09:49.798
There is no excuse
for such beastly behavior, but…

09:51.508 --> 09:55.720
It's just that I adore you so
and it's painful living far away from you.

09:58.014 --> 10:01.309
So when, you chose a rave
over our composing time, well…

10:02.102 --> 10:05.939
it just made me very sad
to see our special bond fade.

10:07.857 --> 10:11.653
‐ But, Dante, our bond cannot fade.

10:12.654 --> 10:14.239
‐ It… it can't?

10:14.531 --> 10:15.990
‐ Of course not.

10:16.533 --> 10:18.326
We are the Crescendo Brothers.

10:18.326 --> 10:20.161
No matter what comes our way,

10:20.161 --> 10:24.040
be it TrollsTopia
or even the sickest of sick raves,

10:24.582 --> 10:26.543
nothing will ever change that.

10:27.877 --> 10:28.711
‐ Really?

10:32.173 --> 10:33.633
Thank you, Forte.

10:36.219 --> 10:37.804
‐ Oh, and by the way,

10:37.804 --> 10:41.975
the whole reason I wanted us to come here
was to seek inspiration for our symphony.

10:42.225 --> 10:43.184
‐ Truly?

10:43.184 --> 10:45.186
What kind of inspiration?

10:49.607 --> 10:52.944
[ Trolls cheering ]

10:52.944 --> 10:54.487
You were correct, Forte!

10:54.779 --> 10:57.282
The syncopation! The thumping bass!

10:57.282 --> 11:00.994
Techno inspiration
was just what our composition needed!

11:00.994 --> 11:02.745
[ laughing ]

11:02.745 --> 11:05.832
♪

