11:43.953 --> 11:49.209
‐ Ah, Harmonious Hall is the perfect place
for the TrollsTopia art show.

11:49.209 --> 11:52.295
‐ Oh, look, I really like Holly's:

11:52.295 --> 11:54.214
The Troll with the Pearl Earring…

11:55.215 --> 11:56.966
Who Also Has Really Big Hair.

11:57.884 --> 12:02.388
‐ Oh, and who could forget
the Venus de Guy‐lo?

12:02.388 --> 12:03.223
‐ Hi!

12:03.223 --> 12:04.140
[ gasp ]

12:04.140 --> 12:08.519
I figured, why make a statue
when I can display the real work of art?

12:08.895 --> 12:10.104
[ laughing ]

12:10.104 --> 12:11.481
‐ Oh!
‐ Oh!

12:11.814 --> 12:15.401
‐ Mm, every piece just sings to me.

12:15.860 --> 12:16.736
Like that one!

12:18.321 --> 12:19.405
And that one!

12:19.989 --> 12:20.823
And…

12:21.491 --> 12:24.494
Huh? Except for Synth's painting?

12:27.372 --> 12:32.335
‐ Yeah, I mean I like it.
But it just not singing to me.

12:32.460 --> 12:33.336
SYNTH:
Hmm.

12:33.962 --> 12:35.588
POPPY:
Oh, poor Synth.

12:35.588 --> 12:36.798
‐ Ooh!

12:37.799 --> 12:40.551
‐ No. Synth worked really hard
on this painting

12:40.551 --> 12:42.387
and we owe it to him to connect with it.

12:42.762 --> 12:44.889
Maybe we're just not looking at it right.

12:46.266 --> 12:47.684
‐ Ah…
‐ Hmm…

12:47.684 --> 12:48.768
‐ Okay.

12:49.185 --> 12:50.311
‐ Hmm…
‐ Hmm…

12:50.603 --> 12:51.771
Hmm…

