Hmm…

12:53.231 --> 12:55.233
‐ Hmm…

12:55.233 --> 12:56.651
I think I feel something!

12:57.318 --> 12:59.904
‐ Yeah, that would be
the dizziness setting in…

13:01.030 --> 13:04.075
‐ Oh. Oh, oh, ooh!

13:05.827 --> 13:06.744
[ gasp ]

13:06.744 --> 13:08.496
Oh, no, Synth's painting!

13:08.913 --> 13:11.291
‐ Poppy, it's completely busted!

13:11.291 --> 13:12.542
‐ What are we gonna do?

13:13.126 --> 13:15.712
‐ Uh… uh… uh…

13:15.962 --> 13:17.005
We're gonna fix it!

13:17.338 --> 13:20.883
You two cover for me while I act quickly
without thinking things blue!

13:22.051 --> 13:25.138
‐ Pretty sure she meant,
"without thinking things through."

13:25.138 --> 13:27.265
‐ Mmhmm.
Troll better slow down.

13:27.640 --> 13:29.267
♪

13:29.267 --> 13:30.476
‐ Um…

13:36.024 --> 13:37.066
uh…

13:38.609 --> 13:41.237
Uh… uh… uh…

13:41.237 --> 13:44.824
‐ Poppy, look, I like to be as optimistic
as the next Troll,

13:44.824 --> 13:47.535
but there's no way this is gonna…

13:47.535 --> 13:48.578
[ gasp ]

13:50.955 --> 13:53.458
It's amaze‐ba‐bonkers!

13:53.458 --> 13:55.793
It looks the same and yet…

13:55.793 --> 13:58.713
‐ Yeah, I don't know what you did,
Queen P.

13:58.713 --> 14:02.091
But now this painting is sing‐ing‐to‐me!

14:02.550 --> 14:04.635
‐ Really? Do you think Synth will notice?

14:04.635 --> 14:07.930
‐ Yo! How'd I do that, yo?

14:08.389 --> 14:09.307
‐ Phew.

14:09.307 --> 14:13.728
‐ Synth, I had no idea
you had such artistic ambition!

14:13.936 --> 14:17.065
‐ I don't.
I just went all "swippy‐swap!"

14:17.065 --> 14:18.441
with the brush thing and…

14:18.775 --> 14:21.819
created a masterwork
of such power and complexity

14:21.819 --> 14:24.197
it's destined to stand the test of time?

14:25.782 --> 14:27.283
That sound right to anyone?

14:27.283 --> 14:28.910
SKY TORONTO:
Sounds right to me.

14:29.619 --> 14:31.412
Synth, according to my assistant,

14:31.412 --> 14:32.872
my vitals are normal.

14:32.872 --> 14:35.541
So this elevated reaction
I'm having to your piece

14:35.541 --> 14:36.375
can only be…

14:37.251 --> 14:38.169
emotion.

14:38.169 --> 14:39.045
[ all gasp ]

14:39.378 --> 14:42.632
I insist you paint something new
to hang in my office.

14:42.924 --> 14:46.844
‐ All right, sure, I could try
a swippy swap somethin' up for ya.

14:46.844 --> 14:47.845
‐ Excellent.

14:47.845 --> 14:49.847
And I'll take one of those as well.

14:52.308 --> 14:53.810
[ Guy laughing ]

14:55.937 --> 14:57.271
‐ Now what, Poppy?

14:57.271 --> 14:59.690
Technically, you swippy swapped
that painting!

15:00.483 --> 15:01.484
‐ Yeah…

15:01.943 --> 15:04.362
But it could work out, right?

15:04.862 --> 15:08.407
I mean, who knows, Synth's next piece
might blow Sky away!

15:09.367 --> 15:11.160
‐ You ready, Sky Toront‐bro?

15:12.286 --> 15:13.621
Ma‐ma!

15:15.289 --> 15:17.166
‐ Well, cupcakes.

15:17.834 --> 15:18.876
