17:00.019 --> 17:01.145
♪ Make it magical ♪

17:01.145 --> 17:02.438
♪ Let it really sing ♪

17:02.438 --> 17:03.689
♪ With a little love ♪

17:03.689 --> 17:05.524
♪ It's a masterpiece ♪

17:05.983 --> 17:07.360
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

17:07.485 --> 17:08.402
♪ Make it nice ♪

17:08.402 --> 17:10.029
♪ Brush it up, polish it ♪

17:10.029 --> 17:11.948
♪ Not too much, no ♪

17:11.948 --> 17:12.865
♪ Keep it real ♪

17:12.865 --> 17:15.534
♪ Make 'em feel what you feel ♪

17:15.826 --> 17:16.827
♪ Make it sing ♪

17:16.827 --> 17:18.246
♪ Lemme see all the colors ♪

17:18.246 --> 17:19.789
♪ Start dancing ♪

17:19.789 --> 17:20.706
♪ Dancing ♪

17:20.706 --> 17:21.624
♪ Never seen ♪

17:21.624 --> 17:25.044
♪ Anything quite like it before ♪

17:25.378 --> 17:26.963
♪ Put your heart in your art ♪

17:26.963 --> 17:29.340
♪ Break the rules, take some chances ♪

17:29.340 --> 17:30.383
♪ Chances ♪

17:30.383 --> 17:32.218
♪ I'm lookin' at it feel the magic ♪

17:32.218 --> 17:34.178
♪ Of the masterpiece ♪

17:34.178 --> 17:37.014
♪ Make it sing make it sing ♪♪

17:38.849 --> 17:40.726
‐ Oh! Remarkable!

17:40.726 --> 17:42.186
Simply remarkable!

17:43.354 --> 17:46.691
‐ Done. Every single Troll
has a Synth painting they love.

17:46.941 --> 17:48.901
Now this can all be over and‐‐

17:48.901 --> 17:51.946
‐ Synth, seeing all of these
masterful works of art

17:51.946 --> 17:54.865
you have painted confirms
that we Classical Trolls

17:54.865 --> 17:57.410
have selected the right Troll
for the job.

17:58.202 --> 17:59.328
‐ What job?

17:59.620 --> 18:00.830
‐ What job?

18:01.080 --> 18:04.959
‐ We have chosen you to paint
the greatest canvas of all!

18:05.167 --> 18:09.213
The ceiling of Harmonious Hall!

18:09.797 --> 18:11.090
‐ Oh, snap!

18:11.090 --> 18:12.675
‐ Oh, snap.

18:13.092 --> 18:15.553
‐ We have supplies, paints,
and a platform

18:15.553 --> 18:19.348
upon which artists have created
their art for generations.

18:19.348 --> 18:20.558
So…?

18:21.017 --> 18:22.310
‐ Hmm…

18:22.560 --> 18:24.395
‐ Say no, Synth, say no.

18:25.062 --> 18:25.938
‐ Well…

18:26.522 --> 18:29.066
you don't say no
to a platform like that, bro!

18:29.317 --> 18:30.484
Ha‐ha!

18:32.737 --> 18:36.032
Swippy swap, swap swippy, swippity swap,
swap on the swip…

18:36.490 --> 18:37.617
‐ Oh…

18:38.451 --> 18:40.494
[ whispering ]

18:41.746 --> 18:44.707
‐ Hmm, this doesn't appear
to be singing just yet.

18:44.999 --> 18:47.668
But worry not, Synth will prevail!

18:48.169 --> 18:51.172
‐ How can I repaint his work
with everyone watching?

18:51.464 --> 18:52.465
‐ I've got it!

18:52.840 --> 18:56.260
Poppy, how do you feel
about mind‐wiping brain lasers

18:56.260 --> 18:58.304
that can zap away memories?

19:00.348 --> 19:01.682
‐ Not great?

19:02.308 --> 19:03.809
‐ Hmm. Then I don't got it.

19:04.935 --> 19:06.812
‐ Argh, I need a diversion.

19:09.815 --> 19:13.486
Gee, it's a shame there's nothing
to entertain the crowd

19:13.486 --> 19:15.321
while we wait for Synth to finish.

19:15.780 --> 19:19.909
Y'know, Dante, I'll bet the acoustics
in here are incredible…

19:20.117 --> 19:23.162
‐ If you're intimating
that a musical genius such as myself

19:23.162 --> 19:25.706
will simply drop everything
he's doing to conduct

19:25.706 --> 19:27.541
just to amuse the masses…

19:28.584 --> 19:32.088
then consider
your intimations correct, girl!

19:33.839 --> 19:34.882
[ clears his throat ]

19:34.882 --> 19:38.552
♪

19:39.303 --> 19:41.097
‐ Oh!
‐ Oh!

19:41.097 --> 19:44.100
♪

19:59.198 --> 20:02.118
‐ Why isn't it singing?
She's painted everything!

20:02.118 --> 20:03.285
‐ Not everything.

20:03.285 --> 20:05.955
She's still gotta do
Synth's signature, see?

20:08.416 --> 20:09.500
B:
There.

20:10.710 --> 20:11.544
‐ Oh?

20:14.630 --> 20:15.965
‐ Oh!
‐ Oh!

20:15.965 --> 20:17.466
[ celebrating ]

20:17.466 --> 20:20.136
‐ 'Tis a symphony for the eyes!

20:22.555 --> 20:23.389
[ gasp ]

20:23.848 --> 20:25.266
‐ So inspired!

20:25.266 --> 20:28.853
Synth, may I climb up this platform
with you for a closer look?

20:28.853 --> 20:31.313
‐ Uh, I'd advise against it.

20:31.313 --> 20:35.526
That old platform is far too rickety
to hold two Trolls at the same time.

20:36.110 --> 20:37.319
‐ Say what now?

20:37.319 --> 20:38.779
‐ Uh, uh, uh…
‐ Uh, uh, uh…

20:38.779 --> 20:39.947
[ screaming ]

20:39.947 --> 20:41.031
[ gasp ]

20:42.742 --> 20:45.911
‐ Poppy, what were you doing
climbing on that platform, yo?

20:46.746 --> 20:47.705
‐ Uh…

20:47.705 --> 20:50.875
would you believe I went up there
to give you a hug?

20:51.917 --> 20:54.712
‐ Yeah, probably.
If you hadn't said it like that.

20:55.296 --> 20:56.172
‐ Oh.

20:56.505 --> 20:59.508
Well, it's a long story, Synth,

20:59.508 --> 21:00.926
but the truth is…

21:00.926 --> 21:04.847
everything you've painted,
I've been painting over it.

21:05.765 --> 21:07.099
‐ Wait, what?

21:07.099 --> 21:09.935
So, you've been… rearting my art?

21:10.895 --> 21:12.646
‐ Basically, yes.

21:13.522 --> 21:15.566
I don't really understand it but…

21:16.108 --> 21:19.236
for some reason
the combination of your work

21:19.236 --> 21:21.739
and my re‐doing your work…

21:21.739 --> 21:23.491
just made the paintings sing.

21:24.158 --> 21:26.494
And I didn't know how to tell you, so…

21:27.161 --> 21:29.038
I just kept doing it.

21:30.164 --> 21:31.874
‐ Quite the scandal.
‐ What a shock!

21:33.334 --> 21:34.543
‐ Well, Poppy…

21:34.752 --> 21:36.295
if what you say is true…

21:37.254 --> 21:38.422
then that means…

21:39.340 --> 21:41.342
I am very, very relieved!

21:41.842 --> 21:42.676
‐ Huh?

21:43.010 --> 21:44.011
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

21:44.470 --> 21:48.766
‐ It was too much pressure
being TrollsTopia's favorite artist!

21:48.766 --> 21:54.355
Every time I got asked to make a painting,
I worried I couldn't do it all on my own.

21:54.605 --> 21:58.275
But it turns out, I was actually
part of a team the whole time.

21:59.068 --> 22:01.445
And I think that's pretty great, y'know?

22:02.112 --> 22:03.989
‐ Yeah, Synth. I do know.

22:05.699 --> 22:07.034
‐ Aww.
‐ Aww.

22:07.326 --> 22:08.702
‐ Aww.
‐ Aww.

22:09.954 --> 22:10.913
‐ Aww.

22:12.540 --> 22:16.627
‐ You know, now that the ceiling
has been taken care of…

22:16.627 --> 22:21.882
the front courtyard of this hall could use
a new eye‐catching masterpiece.

22:21.882 --> 22:25.094
‐ Ha‐ha! Say no more, Dante.

22:25.094 --> 22:27.555
Team Poppy and Synth are on it, yo!

22:28.597 --> 22:31.183
‐ Oh, no, sorry,
I wasn't talking about you.

22:31.183 --> 22:33.102
I was talking about him.

